text: Lhendup Tshering (born 5 June 1947), is an archer who internationally represented Bhutan Tshering competed for Bhutan at the 1984 Summer Olympics held in Los Angeles in the individual event where he finished 60th.Sports Reference Profile ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic archers of Bhutan Category:Archers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Bhutanese male archers
